data.description: The BEST VALUE in East TN. Anyone looking for lots of space inside and outside at a GREAT PRICE is going to want to come see this AMAZING HOME! The current LARGE FAMILY that calls 3633 Antioch Church home has loved the freedom of living on 2.5 private acres but close to all the amenities of Lenoir City. Now, dad's got a new job so they have to move but here's some of the other things they've loved: TONS OF BEDROOM SPACES, INDOOR BASKETBALL HOOP, KARAOKE STAGE, HUGE OPEN INDOOR SPACES, LAND TO MINI-HOMESTEAD and LET KIDS PLAY, a LARGE WALK-IN PANTRY, and much more!  Schedule your showing today!
